About
=====
This example continues on from simple-wm-composite, it uses the clutter library to create a opengl-based front-end.
NOTE: The same rules apply to starting as the simple-wm example.

Files
=====
config.h  - configurable user defaults
main.c    - entry point of app
keyboard  - handles keyboard events
composite - handles the off-screen render buffer (X11 composite extension)
